  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Datura Time - Unleash Your Heroic Potential in a Retro-3D, Eastern European-Inspired Alternate Reality!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Datura Time is a third-person action-adventure game that catapults you into a realm swirling with mystery, suspense, and dynamic action. This captivating world is a tribute to the 90's console games era, handcrafted with love and passion by a single-developer, Vladeta Stojanovic, with an infusion of post-Soviet and Eastern European aesthetics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You, the player, are plunged into an enigmatic alternative reality known as the \"Zone\" after an accidental encounter with a peculiar drug - \"Datura\". Here, you'll cross paths with a host of characters, some allies, some foes, all delivering a singular message - you are an outsider and the unfolding reality is more than meets the eye. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you navigate this perilous world, you'll unravel the Zone's hidden truths - it's a metaphysical limbo, home to the souls of Eastern Europe and the former Soviet Union, currently under the control of malevolent entities. This sinister realm is in desperate need of a true hero - a role YOU never expected but must now embrace. Your mission? Survive, defeat the wicked forces, restore balance, and return home. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>29 thrilling levels</strong> meticulously designed to challenge skills and advance the story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Post-Soviet Eastern European aesthetics</strong> blending history and imagination for a unique experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Third-person combat</strong> with Balkan-Rambo style or strategic Datura properties.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse enemies and Eastern Bloc weapons</strong> each with distinct abilities and weaknesses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic gameplay paths</strong> - aggressive, stealth, or tactical approaches with different outcomes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rich lore and characters</strong> through intriguing NPC interactions and Zone mysteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nostalgic 90s visuals</strong> with retro 3D graphics honoring classic console games.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/35f4a637c4cec0163643a0cb2dc9c80e.poster.avif?t=1755589794\" width=468 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/35f4a637c4cec0163643a0cb2dc9c80e.webm?t=1755589794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/35f4a637c4cec0163643a0cb2dc9c80e.mp4?t=1755589794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/19d0cd84c730723327a1c03f33e5fd30.poster.avif?t=1755589794\" width=468 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/19d0cd84c730723327a1c03f33e5fd30.webm?t=1755589794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/19d0cd84c730723327a1c03f33e5fd30.mp4?t=1755589794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2425360/extras/6ded79d7a0f98ffc4826e615d6ea0eb1.poster.avif?t=1755589794\" width=468 height=356 ><